{
  "page": "Street of Flies",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Street of Flies</b> is a street in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> where butchers can be found.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Flies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>On the <a href=\"/index.php/Feast_Day_of_Our_Father_Above\" title=\"Feast Day of Our Father Above\">Feast Day of Our Father Above</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>, had the dungeons of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> emptied and all the offenders punished publicly. There were so many prisoners that the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Justice\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King&#39;s Justice\">King's Justice</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Victor_Risley\" title=\"Victor Risley\">Victor Risley</a>, was aided in his task by <a href=\"/index.php/Tessario\" title=\"Tessario\">Tessario</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Fingers_(guards)\" title=\"Fingers (guards)\">Fingers</a>. The court fool <a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a> described the event as looking more like a butchery than execution, and noted that Lord Unwin should have sent for the butchers of the Street of Flies instead of the Hand's Fingers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Street_of_Flies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404185148\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.038 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 918/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 518/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser